'''Torment''' may refer to the following:

* The feeling of pain or [[suffering]].
* Causing to suffer, [[torture]].
* [[Torment (film)|''Torment'' (film)]] (''Hets''), 1944 film, directed by [[Alf Sj<U+00F6>berg]], screenplay by [[Ingmar Bergman]]
* [[Torment (Magic: The Gathering)]], a Magic: The Gathering expansion set released in 2002
* [[Planescape: Torment]], a computer game
* [[Torment (Mechanical Moth album)|''Torment'' (Mechanical Moth album)]], an album by Mechanical Moth
*'''Clothing'''
'''Torment Fight Gear''', a brand of clothing.
